  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="DE">Global Center on Climate Mobility (GCCM). Datenbasierte, vorausschauende Ma&#xDF;nahmen zur Klimamobilit&#xE4;t. (ACMI - African Climate Modelling Initiative)</narrative>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Global Center on Climate Mobility (GCCM). Driving data-based, anticipatory action on climate mobility  (ACMI - African Climate Modelling Initiative)</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="DE">Im Rahmen des Projekts &#x201C;Global Center on Climate Mobility (GCCM) Driving data-based, anticipatory action on climate mobility in Africa and the Caribbean and other regions&#x201D; werden Daten zur Fr&#xFC;herkennung von Klima(wandel)folgen mit Fokus Afrika und Karibik erhoben. Avisiert sind ebenfalls Kapazit&#xE4;ten und Engagement zur Fr&#xFC;herkennung von Klima(wandel)folgen auszubauen. Dies beinhaltet insbesondere durch Klimaauswirkungen bedingte Forced Mobility. Weiterhin sollen f&#xFC;r afrikanische Regierungen und in Abstimmung mit der African Union, anhand zuvor identifizierter potentieller Entwicklungsm&#xF6;glichkeiten, Handlungsoptionen entwickelt werden, den jeweiligen Risiken entgegengewirkt werden, Vulnerabilit&#xE4;ten minimiert und Resilienzen in den betroffenen Kommunen und Bev&#xF6;lkerungsschichten gest&#xE4;rkt werden.</narrative>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Thorugh the &#x201E;Global Center on Climate Mobility (GCCM) Driving data-based, anticipatory action on climate mobility in Africa and the Caribbean and other regions&#x201D; it is expected to collect early warning data on climate risk with a focus on Africa and the Caribbean. Additionally, together with the African Union and local governments and based on the previously identified risks, it is intended to increased capacity and comprehensive engagement to predict climate impacts, including forced mobility, and to take anticipatory action to mitigate risks and reduce vulnerability, create opportunities for harnessing mobility, and build resilience among affected people and communities.</narrative>
  </description>
